rows.label: qst201327_msg0001
rows.name:
I thought this place seemed noisy all of
a sudden. Are you here to rescue us?

rows.label: qst201327_msg0003
rows.name:
I was getting a bit worried, with the
kids with potential shrinking in number
and those without going off somewhere.

rows.label: qst201327_msg0004
rows.name:
But I suppose everything will be all
right now? Thank you very much!

rows.label: qst201327_msg0005
rows.name:
So, I think that's the last of the
kidnapped children, right?

rows.label: qst201327_msg0006
rows.name:
Let's hurry back and meet up
with Tokiha!

rows.label: qst201327_msg0007
rows.name:
Looks like that's the last of
the abducted kids.

rows.label: qst201327_msg0008
rows.name:
We should go find Tokiha.
She might be in trouble!

rows.label: qst201327_msg0009
rows.name:
All kidnapped littlepon nice
and safe now!

rows.label: qst201327_msg0010

I believe we have rescued all of
the kidnapped children now.
